{"tid":1903793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國半天急增 594 宗確診","createTime":"2020-02-29T07:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T08:21:26.000Z","uid":89543,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9a81306a113df8f8384629d761190a5a904ddf3d","tid":1903793,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"韓國今早公佈新增 594 宗新型冠狀病毒確診病例，總數達到 2,931。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，新增的 594 例中，大邱市 476 例、慶尚北道 60 例，首爾市 12 例、釜山市 12 例、仁川市 2 例、蔚山市 3 例、京畿道 4 例、忠清北道 1 例、忠清南道 13 例、全羅南道 1 例、慶尚南道 10 例。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前，死亡病例 16 人，康覆並解除隔離人數為 27 人。<br />\n<br />\n韓國的中央防疫對策本部在每天當地時上午 10 點（香港時間 9 時）和下午 5 點（香港時間 4 時）分別公布截至當天上午 9 點和下午 4 點的疫情信息。昨天兩次公佈合共新增 571 宗確診，是單日新高。今天早上公佈的半天新增病例已達 594 宗，已超越昨天整日數字。"},{"pid":"283faa1344bc1005d4be74765235ea0032c2245c","tid":1903793,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3eedad871b913a64720bb8c7903c6367caf979","tid":1903793,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E-594-%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E-594-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2F&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT28v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=6539f06f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258D%258